Package: serverctl-agent
Version: 1.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: ServerCtl <admin@serverctl.local>
Description: ServerCtl monitoring agent
 Lightweight agent that connects to a ServerCtl backend over WebSocket,
 reports system metrics, and executes remote management commands.
 Supports Debian/Ubuntu and other dpkg-based distributions.
